---
import Layout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | MAUIverse"
  description="Privacy policy for MAUIverse."
  allowPageScroll={true}
>
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 relative z-10">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="fade-in">
      <h1 class="text-gradient text-4xl md:text-6xl font-header font-bold mb-8">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        This privacy policy explains how the MAUIverse collects, uses, and protects your information.
      </p>
      </div>
      <div class="divider-gradient mb-10"></div>
      <div class="reveal">
      <h2 class="text-brand-dark text-2xl font-header font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Newsletter</h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-base mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        When you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your name and email address. We use this information to send you updates about the MAUIverse community. We do not share your data with third parties for marketing purposes. You can unsubscribe at any time via the link in our emails.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted text-base mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        The subscribe form uses Google reCAPTCHA to prevent spam. View their privacy policy and terms of service at the links below.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-2 mb-10 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
        <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand hover:underline">Google Terms of Service</a></li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="text-brand-dark text-2xl font-header font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us via the <a href="/discord/" class="text-brand hover:underline">discord</a>.
      </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
